# Turkish Ocr Service

## docker run

```bash
 docker run -p 5000:5000 monar2/turkish-ocr-service
```

## check service status
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000
```
result
```json
{
  "msg": "UP"
}
```


## to use ocr service

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/loadImage  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"image":"[base64string]"}'
```
result 
```json
{
  "text": "ABC"
}
```


example
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/loadImage \
 -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
 -d '{"image":""}'
```
